BFN 

  [Text] Lieutenant General Mustafa Talas, deputy commander 
in chief of the Army and the Armed Forces, deputy prime 
minister, and defense minister, today received Lieutenant 
General Faruq 'Ali Muhammad, Sudanese deputy chief of staff, and 
the delegation accompanying him. Lieutenant General 'Ali Aslan, 
deputy chief of staff of the Army and the Armed Forces, attended 
the meeting. 
  The talks dealt with relations of cooperation and 
coordination between the fraternal Syrian and Sudanese Armies, 
and the means of promoting these relations in the interest of 
the two fraternal countries. 

